---
const benefits = [
  "Menos requisitos y documentos",
  "Trámites más rápidos y digitales",
  "Reducción de costos y tiempos",
  "Mayor transparencia",
  "Mejor atención ciudadana",
  "Mayor certeza jurídica"
];
---

<section id="beneficios" class="benefits-section">
  <div class="benefits-container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2 class="section-title">Beneficios para la Ciudadanía y las Empresas</h2>
      <p class="section-description" style="font-size: 1.125rem; font-weight: 600; margin-top: 1rem;">
        La Mejora Regulatoria en Tijuana busca generar beneficios concretos:
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="benefits-content">
      <div class="benefits-text">
        <ul class="benefits-list">
          {benefits.map((text) => (
            <li class="benefit-item">
              <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="benefit-icon">
                <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline>
              </svg>
              <span class="benefit-text">{text}</span>
            </li>
          ))}
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="benefits-quote">
        <figure class="quote-card">
          <blockquote class="quote-text">
            La mejora regulatoria no es solo digitalizar, es humanizar el servicio público eliminando barreras innecesarias.
          </blockquote>
        </figure>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .benefits-section {
    padding: 10rem 1.5rem;
    background-color: #383838;
    color: white;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .benefits-container {
    max-width: 80rem;
    margin: 0 auto;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 10;
  }

  .section-header {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .section-overline {
    font-weight: 900;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.3em;
    color: #BA945C;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    line-height: 1.15;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .section-title {
      font-size: 3.5rem;
    }
  }

  .section-description {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9); /* Mejorado contraste de 0.7 a 0.9 */
  }

  .benefits-content {
    display: grid;
    gap: 5rem;
    align-items: center;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .benefits-content {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }

  .benefits-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.5rem;    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;  }

  .benefit-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
  }

  .benefit-icon {
    color: #BA945C;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .benefit-text {
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .benefits-quote {
    position: relative;
  }

  .quote-card {
    background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
    padding: 3rem;
    border-radius: 2rem;
  }

  .quote-text {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    font-style: italic;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }
</style>
